Jolene Blalock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jolene_Blalock 0 Jolene Blalock (born March 5, 1975) is an American actress and model, best known for playing the Vulcan first officer and science officer T'Pol on the UPN science-fiction series Star Trek: Enterprise. She has also guest-starred on television series and films.
